We are looking for a Commodity Analyst (Coal) for the Dubai office of a leading coal mining company with the mines in Russia.

<b>Responsibilities:</b>

- Analysis of the international coal market;

- Formation of conclusions and recommendations for business based on data arrays and preparation of analytical reports for management;

- Analysis of coal markets’ potential in different countries;

- Database maintenance;

- Building forecasts for the market segment.

<b>Requirements:</b>

- Higher economic/technical education and experience as an analyst for at least 2 years;

- Ability to work with large amounts of information;

- Experience in fundamental analysis of the industry;

- Ability to conduct analytical research to test strategic hypotheses;

- Ability to clearly express thoughts and form structured presentations.

Job Type: Full-time

Salary: Rp409,783 - Rp1,697,794 per month

Experience:
 • Coal Analytics: 1 year (Required)

